IN SECURITY?
POLICE ACADEMY.

00:38.238 --> 00:40.807
NAME IS DETECTIVE OUELLETTE,
25th PRECINCT.

00:40.841 --> 00:42.042
MOM, THIS IS ANGELA.

00:42.075 --> 00:43.544
