ALL THE TREES ON THEIR PROPERTY.

02:21.250 --> 02:23.486
IT'S A SOVIET THING ‐‐
MASTERY OVER NATURE.

02:23.519 --> 02:25.688
HEY, PACO, QUIT BOGARTING
ALL THE FRUITY PEBBLES.

02:25.722 --> 02:26.856
UNH ‐‐

02:26.889 --> 02:28.191
