02:29.359 --> 02:31.394
HEY, GUESS HOW MANY, UH,
GLADE PlugIns I GOT YESTERDAY.

02:31.427 --> 02:36.933
UH, STEVIE IS JUST, LIKE,
STARING AT THE TV.

02:36.966 --> 02:38.401
75. AND GUESS HOW MUCH
IT COST ME.

02:38.434 --> 02:40.269
