AND IT <i>IS.</i>

02:47.977 --> 02:49.545
THEY ARE RIGHT.
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

02:49.579 --> 02:53.249
♪♪ OOH, BABY ♪♪

02:53.282 --> 02:55.118
PLEASE GO BACK
TO SCREWING ANDY.

02:55.151 --> 02:57.854
I'M COUPONING
BECAUSE WE HAVE NO MONEY.

02:57.887 --> 03:00.390
