IN THAT FAKE CHARITY,

03:00.423 --> 03:02.225
AND YOU AND ANDY
DON'T MAKE DICK.

03:02.258 --> 03:03.259
I HAVE NO SKILLS.

03:03.292 --> 03:04.994
WE'RE REALLY BROKE?
YEAH.

03:05.028 --> 03:09.132
STEVIE SHOULD BE PLAYING SOCCER,
NOT ‐‐ NOT WATCHING IT.

03:09.165 --> 03:10.500
I TRIED TO ENROLL HIM

03:10.533 --> 03:13.403
IN THAT FANCY CITY LEAGUE
AT ASHFORD PARK,

03:13.436 --> 03:16.339
BUT, APPARENTLY,
I MISSED THE DEADLINE
BY, LIKE, TWO WEEKS.

03:16.372 --> 03:17.640
THOSE UPTIGHT PRICKS...

03:17.673 --> 03:20.977
AUNT NANCY,
SOMEONE NAMED "KIKU" CALLED ‐‐

03:21.010 --> 03:22.078
THREE TIMES.

03:22.111 --> 03:23.112
WHAT DID SHE WANT?

03:23.146 --> 03:24.380
SHE SAID IT WAS PERSONAL.

03:24.414 --> 03:26.649
SHE SOUNDED
LIKE SHE'D BEEN DRINKING.

03:26.683 --> 03:27.850
WHO IS SHE?

03:27.884 --> 03:29.052
DID THE BULLET
MAKE YOU A LESBO?

03:29.085 --> 03:30.620
LESBO?

03:31.921 --> 03:33.523
COME ON, STEVIE.
LET'S GET DRESSED.

03:33.556 --> 03:35.591
WE'RE GONNA GO
SIGN YOU UP FOR SOCCER.

03:35.625 --> 03:36.693
DOES SHE LIKE YOU?

03:36.726 --> 03:37.727
