03:37.760 --> 03:39.195
MM.

03:39.228 --> 03:41.431
YOU'D KNOW, 'CAUSE WOMEN
RELEASE A PHEROMONE.

03:41.464 --> 03:42.765
BULLSHIT.
NO, IT'S TRUE.

03:42.799 --> 03:44.667
YOU SMELL IT WITH YOUR BRAIN,
NOT YOUR NOSE.

03:44.701 --> 03:46.602
BUT THERE ARE
DETECTABLE SIGNS ‐‐

03:46.636 --> 03:48.204
THEIR PUPILS DILATE,

03:48.237 --> 03:50.873
THEIR PELVIS
ORIENTS TOWARDS YOU.

03:50.907 --> 03:52.275
THEY POINT THEIR COOCH
AT YOU?

03:52.308 --> 03:54.610
IT'S INVOLUNTARY.
IT'S LIKE A WEATHER VANE.

03:54.644 --> 03:57.580
LIKE A NEWBORN KANGAROO
CRAWLING TO THE POUCH.

03:57.613 --> 03:58.581
GROSS.

03:58.614 --> 04:00.249
WE'RE ALL JUST ANIMALS,
SHANE ‐‐

04:00.283 --> 04:01.451
RED IN TOOTH AND CLAW.

04:01.484 --> 04:03.319
WHY ARE YOU SO NERVOUS,
ANYWAY?

04:03.353 --> 04:04.821
I REALLY LIKE THIS GIRL.

04:06.022 --> 04:08.825
[ BUZZING ]

04:08.858 --> 04:10.259
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

04:10.293 --> 04:12.795
[ DOG BARKS ]

04:14.297 --> 04:17.400
SEE YOU LATER, MAN.
GOOD WORK.

04:17.433 --> 04:19.669
I KNOW.
TAKE HER ON A DOUBLE DATE.

04:19.702 --> 04:22.872
THAT'LL ALLEVIATE THE PRESSURE
OF HAVING TO BE...

04:22.905 --> 04:24.741
YOU KNOW ‐‐
A NORMAL PERSON.

04:24.774 --> 04:25.808
CAN YOU COME?

04:25.842 --> 04:27.510
MM, SORRY, BUDDY.

04:27.543 --> 04:30.213
ME AND JILL ARE ON THE SKIDS ‐‐
SPLITSVILLE.

04:30.246 --> 04:33.716
HOW WAS SHE IN THE SACK ‐‐
AUNT JILL?

04:33.750 --> 04:35.651
YOU ARE SO BROKEN.

04:36.886 --> 04:38.855
DID YOU JUST HAVE
A SLEEPOVER?

04:38.888 --> 04:40.490
SHUT UP.
WE WERE WORKING LATE.

04:40.523 --> 04:41.991
WORKING
ON EACH OTHER'S DICKS.

04:42.025 --> 04:45.228
HEY, HOW'S
YOUR NARCO GIRLFRIEND?

04:45.261 --> 04:47.397
OR DID SHE FINALLY NOTICE
THE COLD, DEAD MARBLES

04:47.430 --> 04:48.731
WHERE YOUR EYES SHOULD BE?

04:48.765 --> 04:51.134
WE HAPPEN TO BE GOING
ON A DOUBLE DATE TONIGHT,

04:51.167 --> 04:52.135
SO FUCK YOURSELF.

04:52.168 --> 04:53.336
KISS MY ASS.

04:53.369 --> 04:55.238
NOT WITH YOUR FRIEND'S JIZZ
ALL OVER IT.

04:55.271 --> 04:57.840
AWW. I MISS MY BROTHER.
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

04:57.874 --> 04:59.042
SHIT.

04:59.075 --> 05:00.943
I GOT TO GO
TO THE DERBY TRACK.

05:00.977 --> 05:02.545
WOULD YOU TELL JILL
I'LL BE GO‐‐

05:02.578 --> 05:03.579
NEVER MIND.

05:03.613 --> 05:06.115
SHE DOESN'T CARE.
NEITHER DO YOU.

05:06.149 --> 05:07.517
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

05:12.955 --> 05:14.223
LOOK AT THESE PEOPLE ‐‐

05:14.257 --> 05:16.392
MOVING IN,
RUINING THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

05:16.426 --> 05:19.262
I KNOW.
IT'S A GODDAMN SHAME.

05:20.763 --> 05:21.931
I'M REALLY SORRY,

05:21.964 --> 05:23.900
BUT BOTH THE NINJAS
AND THE TRANSFORMERS

05:23.933 --> 05:25.301
ALREADY HAVE FULL SQUADS.

05:25.334 --> 05:28.004
PLEASE DON'T PUNISH MY KID
FOR MY SISTER'S SCREW‐UP.

05:28.037 --> 05:29.172
SCREW‐UP?

05:29.205 --> 05:30.640
APPARENTLY,
SHE MISSED THE CUTOFF.

05:30.673 --> 05:33.376
OH. NO. NO, NO, NO, NO.
THEY JUST TELL PEOPLE THAT.

05:33.409 --> 05:36.512
LOOK, OLD SANDWICH
IS A WEALTHY PLACE.

05:36.546 --> 05:38.614
THERE'S A HIGH DEMAND
FOR SLOTS ON OUR TEAMS,

05:38.648 --> 05:40.550
AND THEY USUALLY END UP
GOING TO FAMILIES

05:40.583 --> 05:43.786
WHO ARE ABLE TO MAKE
SIZABLE DONATIONS.

05:43.820 --> 05:46.255
KICKBACKS?
IN YOUTH SOCCER?

05:46.289 --> 05:49.459
SO, UNLESS THAT'S
GONNA BE FEASIBLE, THEN...

05:49.492 --> 05:51.828
THERE IS ANOTHER LEAGUE
DOWN IN HARTFORD.

05:51.861 --> 05:54.430
[ CHUCKLES ]
NO, I GOT YOU, GORDON.

05:54.464 --> 05:55.832
[ CAMERA CLICKS ]
UNDERSTOOD.

05:55.865 --> 05:57.100
