05:57.133 --> 05:59.502
UH, THIS IS A ‐‐
A "WHITES ONLY" LEAGUE.

05:59.535 --> 06:03.473
T‐THIS IS NOT...
A "WHITES ONLY" LEAGUE.

06:03.506 --> 06:05.608
HEY, I DON'T LIKE MEXICANS,
EITHER.

06:05.641 --> 06:07.610
I JUST HAPPENED TO HAVE
GOTTEN KNOCKED UP BY ONE.

06:07.643 --> 06:11.114
THE SPERM, THOUGH ‐‐
IT IS MUY MACHO.

06:11.147 --> 06:12.415
[ CAMERA CLICKS ]
VAMOS, CARINO.

06:12.448 --> 06:13.950
WE NEED TO GO TALK
TO THE LOCAL NEWSPAPER.

06:13.983 --> 06:16.352
WHAT DID YOU SAY YOUR LAST NAME
WAS, AGAIN, GORDON? OR WHAT?

06:16.386 --> 06:17.920
WAIT, WAIT.
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

06:19.489 --> 06:22.191
HEY! HOW WOULD YOU
LIKE TO BE A NINJA?

06:22.225 --> 06:23.593
YEAH.
YEAH.

06:23.626 --> 06:25.495
COME ON. LET'S GO FIND YOU
A UNIFORM, BUDDY.

06:28.231 --> 06:30.266
OH. HERE.

06:34.904 --> 06:37.173
USED TO HAVE ONE
JUST LIKE IT.

06:38.274 --> 06:39.575
[ SIREN WAILING ]

06:39.609 --> 06:40.877
HOW ARE YOU?

06:40.910 --> 06:43.012
CRAMPING, BLOATED.

06:43.046 --> 06:45.081
OH, I'M SORRY.
OR...CONGRATULATIONS.

06:45.114 --> 06:46.416
I‐I DON'T KNOW.

06:50.386 --> 06:51.487
CLEAR!

06:51.521 --> 06:53.856
SO, I GUESS THAT MEANS
YOU CAN'T GO OUT TONIGHT?

06:53.890 --> 06:55.324
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

06:55.358 --> 06:57.293
WOMEN CAN ACCOMPLISH
A SHOCKING NUMBER OF THINGS

06:57.326 --> 07:00.396
WHILE SLOUGHING
ENDOMETRIAL LINING, SHANE.

07:02.832 --> 07:04.734
CLEAR!

07:04.767 --> 07:07.470
I WAS THINKING A DOUBLE DATE ‐‐
OR DOUBLE HANG.

07:07.503 --> 07:09.939
NOT DATE,
WHATEVER YOU WANT TO CALL IT.

07:12.975 --> 07:14.143
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

07:14.177 --> 07:17.246
WAIT ‐‐
SO, NOT A DATE?

07:17.280 --> 07:19.082
Man on P. A.:
<i>CADET MULLEN, YOU'RE DEAD.</i>

07:19.115 --> 07:20.416
SON OF A WHORE!

07:22.118 --> 07:24.687
I'M CONFUSED.
IS ‐‐ IS THAT A YES?

07:24.721 --> 07:27.323
YEAH. OKAY.

07:29.692 --> 07:31.361
<i>CUT IT OUT, ROOKIES.</i>

07:34.497 --> 07:36.199
Andy: HELLO?

07:37.633 --> 07:39.535
HELLO?

07:40.670 --> 07:41.738
WHAT THE HELL?

07:48.611 --> 07:50.246
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

07:50.279 --> 07:54.183
IT IS A SHOCKINGLY COMMON
OCCURRENCE IN MY LIFE

07:54.217 --> 07:56.519
THAT WOMEN ARE GIFTED
UNTO ME,

07:56.552 --> 08:00.323
SEEMINGLY WITH
VERY LITTLE EFFORT ON MY PART.

08:00.356 --> 08:03.259
AND AT A CERTAIN POINT,
AFTER THE LUDICROUS BOUNTY,

08:03.292 --> 08:05.528
YOU HAVE TO FINALLY WONDER,
"WHY?"

08:05.561 --> 08:06.896
OKAY.

08:06.929 --> 08:13.002
IS IT BECAUSE I'M SO JUST
BASELINE PHYSICALLY ATTRACTIVE?

08:13.036 --> 08:14.237
DEBATABLE.

08:14.270 --> 08:17.840
MORE LIKELY,
IT'S 'CAUSE OF THIS ‐‐

08:17.874 --> 08:18.941
KARMA.

08:18.975 --> 08:21.644
I MOTHERFUCKING
EARNED IT.

08:21.678 --> 08:25.581
I WAS THE FECAL MOLECULE
OF A MAGGOT 50 LIVES AGO ‐‐

08:25.615 --> 08:28.317
49 LIVES AGO,
A PARASITE ON A SEA CUCUMBER ‐‐

08:28.351 --> 08:32.889
WORKED MY WAY UP FROM THERE,
PAYING MY REINCARNATORY DUES ‐‐

08:32.922 --> 08:36.392
CORAL, AN EARWIG, A SEWER RAT,

08:36.426 --> 08:40.263
A GRACKLE, GUINEA FOWL,
CLOWN FISH, OCELOT,

08:40.296 --> 08:45.001
EVENTUALLY VAULTING UP
THE EVOLUTIONARY CHAIN TO DOG,

08:45.034 --> 08:47.136
BUT LIKE A SHITTY SMALL DOG

08:47.170 --> 08:50.540
FELLED IMMEDIATELY
BY PARVO OR CANINE SIDS,

08:50.573 --> 08:54.944
MONKEY, MONKEY, DOWN TO OTTER,
MONKEY, CHIMP,

08:54.977 --> 08:56.813
AND THEN FINALLY HUMAN!

08:56.846 --> 08:58.214
BUT ‐‐ WHOOPS! FUCK!

08:58.247 --> 09:01.818
I'M A CHILD SEX SLAVE,
AND I LIVE IN A WELL.

09:01.851 --> 09:06.923
BUT IN ALL THESE INCARNATIONS...

09:06.956 --> 09:11.627
I WAS GOOD AND KIND AND HUMBLE
AND ACCEPTED MY FATE PATIENTLY.

09:11.661 --> 09:12.962
SO, THUS,

09:12.995 --> 09:18.768
AFTER AN ENDLESS SERIES
OF SHORT, OFT BRUTAL LIVES,

09:18.801 --> 09:24.273
I WAS FINALLY, FINALLY,
FINALLY BORN AS ME ‐‐

09:24.307 --> 09:28.411
ANDREW BOTWIN,
EFFORTLESS RECEIVER OF TAIL.

09:28.444 --> 09:31.581
IT'S JUST A THEORY,
OF COURSE.

09:31.614 --> 09:34.984
BUT IF IT'S NOT BIOLOGY
AND IT'S NOT KARMA,

09:35.018 --> 09:37.754
THEN THERE IS A PUPPET MASTER
OUT THERE

09:37.787 --> 09:41.024
WHO ENJOYS WATCHING ME
GET MY FREAK ON ‐‐

09:41.057 --> 09:43.292
AND THAT WOULD MEAN GOD,
BASICALLY ‐‐

09:43.326 --> 09:49.465
AND I WOULD HAVE TO RETHINK,
WELL...EVERYTHING.

09:49.499 --> 09:52.168
IF YOU CAN CATCH ME,
YOU CAN FUCK ME.

09:54.203 --> 09:56.806
YEAH,
I'LL GET MY SKATES.

09:59.340 --> 10:01.475
THIS IS
MY THIRD TIME AROUND.

10:01.509 --> 10:04.445
IT'S MY FIRST ‐‐
BEST DECISION I EVER MADE.

10:04.478 --> 10:06.914
IS IT A DECISION?
I MEAN, I GUESS IT IS.

10:06.947 --> 10:09.116
BUT EVEN WHEN IT IS,
IS IT <i>REALLY?</i>

10:09.150 --> 10:12.520
ALL I KNOW IS, I WAS 100%
SELF‐CENTERED BEFORE COLBY,

10:12.553 --> 10:14.788
AND NOW
EVERYTHING'S ABOUT <i>HIM.</i>

10:15.756 --> 10:20.127
HUSTLE, COLBY!
MAKE DADDY PROUD, BUDDY.

10:20.161 --> 10:21.462
NICE ORANGE‐SLICING.

10:21.495 --> 10:22.696
WHICH ONE'S YOURS?

10:22.730 --> 10:24.965
THE, UH, SLOW IDIOT

10:24.999 --> 10:26.867
WHO JUST GOT SMOKED
BY THAT NEW KID.

10:26.901 --> 10:28.536
WHO IS THAT?
SOME HOUSEKEEPER'S KID?

10:28.569 --> 10:30.371
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT HE'S FAST.

10:32.840 --> 10:34.008
SOMEBODY COVER HIM!

10:34.041 --> 10:36.443
GO, GO, GO, GO!
STEVIE, GO, GO, GO, GO!

10:36.477 --> 10:37.578
OH! WHOO!

10:37.611 --> 10:38.913
UGH!
UGH!UGH!

10:38.946 --> 10:41.182
GOOD BOY!

10:41.215 --> 10:43.317
GORDON.
[ SNAPS FINGERS ]

10:44.718 --> 10:47.054
[ Laughing ]
YOU ARE SO GOOD!

10:47.087 --> 10:49.723
