ARE YOU HAVING FUN?

10:49.757 --> 10:52.026
COME ON, NEW KID.

10:52.059 --> 10:54.428
UM...HI.

10:54.461 --> 10:57.231
YOUR SON'S GONNA BE IN THE GOAL
FOR THE REST OF THE MATCH.

10:57.264 --> 10:58.632
WHY?

10:58.666 --> 11:00.801
'CAUSE HE'S MAKING OUR SONS
LOOK LIKE SACKS OF SHIT.

11:00.835 --> 11:02.169
COMPETITION'S HEALTHY.

11:02.203 --> 11:03.437
A FAIR COMPETITION.

11:03.470 --> 11:05.272
YOUR SON HAS
AN UNNATURAL ADVANTAGE.

11:05.306 --> 11:08.008
