GRAPEFRUIT.

11:10.845 --> 11:12.646
[ Laughing ]
JESUS, JEFF.

11:12.680 --> 11:15.850
SO, WHAT DO YOU SAY?

11:15.883 --> 11:18.252
GOALIE'S A FUN POSITION.

11:18.285 --> 11:19.253
SURE. WHY NOT.

11:19.286 --> 11:20.721
STEVIE.

11:25.359 --> 11:26.694
Okay, go on.

11:26.727 --> 11:29.730
LISTEN, I'M SORRY ABOUT JEFF.
HE'S AN ASSHOLE.

11:29.763 --> 11:33.601
Woman:
GO, GO, GO, GO! GO!

11:33.634 --> 11:34.969
OH, JESUS CHRIST.

11:38.105 --> 11:38.973
UGH!
UGH!UGH!

11:39.006 --> 11:40.908
OH, SWEET MARY...
SON OF A...

11:40.941 --> 11:42.977
