JUST IN HIS NATURE.

11:43.010 --> 11:46.814
SO, WE'LL BE GETTING
THAT DONATION FROM YOU SOON?

11:46.847 --> 11:50.017
OH, GORDON,
WHAT WOULD THE NEWSPAPER SAY?

11:50.050 --> 11:51.819
HE OWNS THE PAPER.

11:51.852 --> 11:54.522
I'M ON THE TEAM NOW!
I'M A NINJA!

11:54.555 --> 11:57.791
DONATION ‐‐ NO PROBLEM.

11:59.126 --> 12:02.796
SO, I WAS READING ABOUT
A 420 AFFILIATE PROGRAM

12:02.830 --> 12:05.065
WHERE YOUR WEBSITE IS LINKED
IN CROSS‐PROMOTIONS

12:05.099 --> 12:07.067
WITH OTHER
MARIJUANA‐BASED SITES.

12:07.101 --> 12:08.002
I SIGNED US UP.

12:08.035 --> 12:09.303
ARE YOU
FUCKING KIDDING ME?

12:09.336 --> 12:11.205
NO. WHY? WHAT?

12:11.238 --> 12:12.740
WE'RE ARTISANS, SILAS.

