24:41.969 --> 24:44.071
AND YOU KNOW
WHAT THE COOL THING IS?

24:44.104 --> 24:47.474
UNLIKE BAPTISM,
IN TEVILAH,

24:47.507 --> 24:50.711
YOU GET ENDLESS CHANCES
TO BE NEW.

24:54.848 --> 24:57.918
I THOUGHT I WAS NEW,
BUT...

24:57.951 --> 25:00.487
MAYBE IT WAS
JUST THE VICODIN.

25:03.991 --> 25:06.460
I CAN'T KEEP MAKING
THE SAME CHOICES.

25:08.996 --> 25:10.297
THEN DON'T.

25:25.846 --> 25:28.048
THE FUCK?!

25:29.883 --> 25:31.051
UNH!

25:31.084 --> 25:32.185
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH MY PLANTS?

25:32.219 --> 25:33.854
I JUST GOT BACK
FROM MY DATE.

25:33.887 --> 25:34.755
BULLSHIT.

25:34.788 --> 25:35.956
WANT TO SMELL MY FINGERS?

25:35.989 --> 25:37.257
SOMETHING HAPPENED
TO YOUR PLANTS?

25:37.291 --> 25:38.592
WHY DON'T YOU ASK
YOUR WEIRDO FRIEND?

25:43.597 --> 25:45.332
WHAT'S GOING ON?

25:46.533 --> 25:48.168
WHAT THE FUCK?!

25:49.069 --> 25:50.404
CODE BREAKER!

25:50.437 --> 25:52.573
I DIDN'T MEAN TO!

25:52.606 --> 25:55.042
I GUESS WE'RE EVEN.

25:57.010 --> 25:58.645
NOT COOL!

25:58.679 --> 25:59.980
[ BELLS JINGLE ]

26:00.013 --> 26:00.981
R.J.!

26:01.014 --> 26:01.982
HELLO?!

26:02.015 --> 26:03.217
R.J.: WE'RE CLOSED.

26:03.250 --> 26:04.818
THE FUCK
ARE MY PLANTS?

26:04.851 --> 26:06.954
WHOA.

26:06.987 --> 26:08.155
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

26:08.188 --> 26:09.656
OH, I REALIZED
I COULD FEEL THINGS AGAIN,

26:09.690 --> 26:11.325
SO I ASKED THIS DUDE TO PUNCH ME
IN THE FACE A COUPLE TIMES,

26:11.358 --> 26:13.627
AND, UH,
HE WENT A LITTLE OVERBOARD.

26:13.660 --> 26:15.229
WELL, WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU, MAN? ARE YOU ON DRUGS?

26:15.262 --> 26:17.097
THAT'S THE POINT.
NOT ANYMORE.

26:17.130 --> 26:19.833
MY PARENTS HAVE BEEN DRUGGING ME
SINCE I WAS 13,

26:19.867 --> 26:21.969
BUT I'M DONE
WEARING THEIR BLINDERS.

26:22.002 --> 26:23.971
JUST GIVE ME MY PLANTS,
MAN.

26:24.004 --> 26:26.940
I LIKED YOU.
I THOUGHT YOU WERE KINDRED.

26:26.974 --> 26:29.243
BUT IT TURNS OUT
YOU'RE AN OAF.

26:29.276 --> 26:31.078
YOU HAVE
NO IMAGINATION.

26:31.111 --> 26:36.283
YOU SEE IT AS DRUGS ‐‐
TO PUSH, LIKE IT'S MERCH.

26:36.316 --> 26:40.621
LIKE MY PARENTS' PILLS ‐‐
CRASS, DEAD, MERCH.

26:42.656 --> 26:44.491
BUT IT'S NOT DEAD.

26:44.525 --> 26:47.961
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S ALIVE.
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S ANCIENT.

26:47.995 --> 26:50.531
IT KNOWS THINGS.

26:50.564 --> 26:53.100
THE PLANTS PICK <i>YOU.</i>

26:53.133 --> 26:57.971
BUT YOU HAVE TO BE READY.
IT IS A BATTLE.

26:58.005 --> 26:59.973
YOU CONTROL <i>THEM</i>
OR THEY CONTROL <i>YOU,</i>

27:00.007 --> 27:01.441
AND i‐I SAW IT TODAY.

27:01.475 --> 27:04.011
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND
THE GIFT YOU HAVE,

27:04.044 --> 27:06.513
AND YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND
THE PLANTS.

27:09.149 --> 27:11.084
THEY FUCKING
TAKE YOU DOWN.

27:11.118 --> 27:13.720
IT WOULD END BADLY
FOR YOU.

27:15.255 --> 27:18.091
YOU COULDN'T SEE IT,
BUT I COULD,

27:18.125 --> 27:20.093
SO NOW THEY'RE ALL GONE.

27:20.127 --> 27:22.763
YOU CAN THANK ME LATER...

27:22.796 --> 27:24.965
OR DON'T.

27:24.998 --> 27:27.501
I DON'T NEED YOU
ANYMORE.

